{
  "title": "Nutty Fluffy Almond Middle Eastern Stir-fry",
  "description": "A post-workout dish featuring almond flour and a touch of grand marnier for a creamy texture, perfect for those low-fat-friendly meals.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
